<anchor id="certmgr_8h_1CertMgr"/> <simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>Certification manager handles the broker switching. It uses the <ulink url="https://docs.nordicsemi.com/bundle/ncs-latest/page/nrf/libraries/modem/modem_key_mgmt.html">Modem key management library</ulink> provided by nordic semicondutor with its <ulink url="https://docs.nordicsemi.com/bundle/nrf-apis-latest/page/group_modem_key_mgmt.html">API</ulink> to write the certificates to the modem. And it uses the <ulink url="https://github.com/littlefs-project/littlefs">littlefs library</ulink> provided by <ulink url="https://docs.zephyrproject.org/latest/samples/subsys/fs/littlefs/README.html#littlefs">Zephyr</ulink> to support file operations.</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="remark"><para>This source code is confidential and proprietary information of AXO Track GmbH, Berlin. You may not disclose, copy, or distribute this source code or any part thereof without the explicit permission of AXO Track GmbH, Berlin. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
